--------------------------------------Finance Performance Suite Presentation Dashboard---------------------------------------------------

This is a self-contained, interactive HTML5 presentation designed to pitch the key insights from your Power BI financial model directly in any web browser—no PowerPoint or Power BI installation required.

The Goal :
It translates raw data from `Financial Sample.xlsx` into a polished, executive-ready story.

The Design :
Features a modern, dark-themed $1280 \times 720\text{px}$ (16:9) responsive layout optimized for sharp presentation screens.


---------------- Interactive Highlights : --------------

Star-Schema Blueprint :
An interactive visualizer showing how your sales tables and dimensions connect.

Executive KPIs : 
Clickable metric cards that drill down into Sales ($110.78M), Orders (1M), and Profit Margins (13.68%).

Seasonality Trend Chart :
A monthly bar chart that highlights peak revenue periods like October ($25.11M).

Segment Leakage Auditor :
Interactive toggle buttons comparing highly profitable Channel Partners (72.87% margin) against bleeding Enterprise segments (-3.74% margin loss).

Terminal Actions :
A built-in terminal setup code block with a one-click copy button for local development.
